subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description:
This Project is support for the Regional Project on Decreasing Vulnerability of Roma which output is:
Poverty reduction in targeted Roma communities through ensuring improved and sustainable social inclusion, better employment and development oppotunities with special focus on strenghtening Roma community.
subproject.title: Decreasing Vulnerability of Ro
